channel.title: Seer's Village Party Room Moved To Falador!
channel.description:
[center]Have you guys seen the Party Room from Seer's Village moved to falador? Now free-players can also make drop partys in the party room, hell ya its fun :D.. Ill post a picture: [img]http://img98.imageshack.us/img98/4757/faladorlocation3le3.jpg[/img] ^This is a map picture.
Now ill post some inside pictures:
[img]http://img98.imageshack.us/img98/2244/chestru4.jpg[/img] ^Now here can u see the chest outside and inside(its not like that, i just putted 2 pictures together) There yelling "Willow Comp" because someone putted like 5 times willow comp in the chest.. and i got nothing. *SAD*
[img]http://img479.imageshack.us/img479/9567/knightsai4.jpg[/img] ^And here the dancing knights (it costs 500gp to let them dance)
[img]http://img479.imageshack.us/img479/1383/balloonsui7.jpg[/img] ^And here were the baloons fall down and humans go psychopat and *POPS* them.. (it cost 1000gp to do that baloons fall down)
Please leave a comment..
~Loadinq1[/center]
